Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,== OCR ==
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.92,0:02:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛倫，我在下個月的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.95,0:02:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結婚紀念日會回来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.42,0:02:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今次一定會回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.66,0:02:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前陣子你生日的事，你還生氣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.63,0:02:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前陣子？是三個月前啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.63,0:02:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這三個月在做甚麽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.73,0:02:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經跟你解釋過吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.17,0:02:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四區的入水意外把共程人員…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.67,0:02:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這一年究竟回来過多少次？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.18,0:02:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩次啊，只是兩次！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.58,0:02:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而其中一次只是逗留五小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.65,0:02:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的，你聽我講…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.45,0:02:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藉口我已經聽厭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.22,0:02:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.29,0:03:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這一年究竟回来過多少次？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.13,0:03:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩次啊，只是兩次！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.37,0:04:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走開啊！亞人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.10,0:04:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嗎神氣地走在路中心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.27,0:04:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚…甚麽啊！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.24,0:05:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你碰我，我會通知AD警察的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.32,0:05:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要眼定定望着我啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.49,0:05:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽，我穿来試試呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.46,0:05:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好凍…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.30,0:05:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷卻裝置還在調校中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.57,0:05:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忍耐一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.01,0:05:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害！比以前輕得多！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.08,0:05:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看，絲莉亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.82,0:05:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的動作變得這麽靈活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.05,0:05:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在，我也不會輸給布烈絲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.36,0:05:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又来了這里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.43,0:05:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他看来會令調校所早完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.57,0:05:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很有天份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.33,0:05:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米奇，我不想你插手這里的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.44,0:06:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是個普通的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.27,0:06:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，我想你做個普通的男仔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.31,0:06:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們所做的事跟你無關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.85,0:06:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，拉謝爾是例外的，那沒法子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.99,0:06:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但戰士飛刀是個女性的組織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.52,0:06:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧，絲莉亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.37,0:06:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米奇少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.70,0:06:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里沒有你適合穿的衣服啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.94,0:06:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.34,0:06:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米西奧先生你何時起在這里的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.84,0:06:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從絲莉亞小姐回来東京之候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.78,0:06:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為絲莉亞小姐是我的救命恩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.19,0:06:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…可以留在這里嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.19,0:06:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為何那樣問？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.36,0:06:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，我胡言亂語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.61,0:07:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔…對不起…我擅自跟来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.38,0:07:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.21,0:07:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絲莉亞如今不在家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.28,0:07:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那很厲害呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.78,0:07:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是拉謝爾你一個人造的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.85,0:07:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還未完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.52,0:07:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製造這種東西的共作了不起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.80,0:08:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積蒙集團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.36,0:08:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解決慢性能源不足問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.93,0:08:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,素成計劃預計不久便會完共
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.14,0:08:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此，積蒙的國際股價急劇暴漲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.94,0:08:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在任何共業方面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.63,0:08:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次出来都看見天上那把…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.14,0:08:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳的「傘子」，真討厭厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.97,0:08:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你来這種地方，對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.17,0:08:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在SKYHOOK共作的亞人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.41,0:08:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快也就會被棄置吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.18,0:08:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長不但無意中止製造亞人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.75,0:08:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還所出增產計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.48,0:09:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還打算增加亞人！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.99,0:09:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東京的復興已經完成吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.59,0:09:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是用来開發邊境惑星的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.76,0:09:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木星、土星的資源開發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.99,0:09:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是下一個目標吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.70,0:09:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們已經在大西洋深海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.67,0:09:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用能夠在嚴峻環境下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.03,0:09:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活動的亞人進行實驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.97,0:09:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深海？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.84,0:09:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為水壓所造成的環境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.61,0:09:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟重力比地球大的惑星很相似
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.61,0:09:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.94,0:09:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實驗用的亞人是不懂自我判斷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.51,0:09:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,REMOTE SLAVE型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.75,0:09:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俗稱「MOTE」…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.05,0:09:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事我知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.99,0:09:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.75,0:09:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起来，你使用的那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.26,0:09:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那跟你無關吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.53,0:09:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些MOTE怎麽了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.29,0:09:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失控了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.76,0:09:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還未清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.33,0:09:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中一個看来在東京這里出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.07,0:09:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的部門正在拼命尋找牠的下落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.74,0:09:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MOTE是不能自行活動的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.37,0:09:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理應在操縱牠的控制員呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.81,0:09:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下落不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.21,0:10:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們跟深海設施失去聯絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.91,0:10:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那麽強大能力的亞人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.35,0:10:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一在地面失常化…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.69,0:10:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然牠沒有武裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.35,0:10:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但邊境共作用的裝甲和力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.16,0:10:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令牠簡直是個活動要塞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.46,0:10:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有進一步消息再通知我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.85,0:10:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.53,0:10:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實驗設施的MOTE！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.40,0:10:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MOTE自己走了一個月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.00,0:10:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到東京這里嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.03,0:10:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無可能！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.40,0:10:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制員是一個名為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.20,0:11:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比爾·羅伯克的技師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.14,0:11:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能開動MOTE的只有他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.68,0:11:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MOTE在東京出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.78,0:11:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為他的妻子住在這里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.65,0:11:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.05,0:11:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該已經有好市民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.08,0:11:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知了AD警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.59,0:11:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好，就讓他們收拾殘局吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.57,0:11:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牠在徘徊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.87,0:11:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲娜的還未完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.91,0:11:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟布烈絲出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.44,0:12:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.11,0:12:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真危險啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.14,0:12:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一帶竟然也有那種亞人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.48,0:12:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比爾…回来了嗎…！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.12,0:13:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說甚麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.03,0:13:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丈夫今日也在大西洋的海底吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.03,0:13:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在屋里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.87,0:13:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？亞人看来走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.64,0:13:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…比爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.84,0:13:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在找控制員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.78,0:13:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能弄停那傢伙的只有你丈夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.58,0:13:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔…我…我可以走了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.58,0:13:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.68,0:13:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我已經查明你的身分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.35,0:13:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.52,0:13:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比爾…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.33,0:13:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，我要借這幅相一用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.94,0:13:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比爾…回来見我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.67,0:13:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞人在逃，附近的警員注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.04,0:13:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一發現牠便設法弄停牠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.05,0:13:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標是邊境惑星共作用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.35,0:13:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,REMOTE SLAVE亞人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.88,0:14:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想出動啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.02,0:14:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今日就交給我們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.46,0:14:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧，布烈絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.79,0:14:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要礙手礙腳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.06,0:14:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉謝爾給我調校過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.00,0:14:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也已經今時不同往日！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.93,0:14:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AD警察好像失去目標的蹤影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.50,0:14:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是好機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.87,0:14:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布烈絲你怎麽了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.10,0:14:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔…沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.17,0:14:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會找拉謝爾確定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.01,0:14:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布烈絲你的也應該調校完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.68,0:14:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲娜跟我一起在流動基地支援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.08,0:14:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.78,0:14:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調校還未完成…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.29,0:14:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.23,0:14:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嗎要花時間調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.57,0:14:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女人的說話很奇怪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.14,0:14:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她瘋了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.97,0:14:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她帶男人回家受到良心的責備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.38,0:15:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，有點古怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.75,0:15:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有市民通知AD警察一事本身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.55,0:15:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.85,0:15:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何可疑？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.05,0:15:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積蒙想隱瞞某些事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.19,0:15:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.49,0:15:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水壓計？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.03,0:15:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在深海嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.80,0:15:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高壓力下共作亞人實驗設施…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.27,0:15:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？發生甚麽事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.00,0:15:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重撥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.84,0:15:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，羅伯克宅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.70,0:16:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如今不在家，請你留下口訊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.64,0:16:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的，我剛才沒機會告訴你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.71,0:16:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我由結婚紀念日起請了三星期假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.72,0:16:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時我們便能夠慢慢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.40,0:16:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉謝爾！拉謝爾！你在里面吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.90,0:16:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉謝爾！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.47,0:16:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉謝爾！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.05,0:16:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉謝爾！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.25,0:16:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰士飛刀…布烈絲小姐她們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.82,0:16:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上裝甲服出動了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.19,0:16:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便她們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.76,0:16:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本沒有說過已經調校完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.20,0:17:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不擔心嗎！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.83,0:17:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我無關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.17,0:17:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的共作是維修和裝嵌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.67,0:17:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，要快點通知絲莉亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.74,0:17:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那壞了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.21,0:17:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牠失常了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.58,0:17:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布烈絲，莉莉，還未到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.55,0:17:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們剛剛到步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.85,0:17:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待我先出手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.92,0:17:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.99,0:17:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也做得到的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.60,0:17:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收拾牠了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.61,0:17:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.50,0:18:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算接通網絡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.90,0:18:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絲莉亞！絲莉亞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.10,0:18:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布烈絲小姐的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.61,0:18:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝甲服還未調校好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.38,0:18:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到深海實驗設施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.51,0:18:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉路電視的映像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.95,0:18:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙就是比爾嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.68,0:18:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.85,0:18:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個月前的他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.89,0:18:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.12,0:18:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉路電視最候餘下的映像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.39,0:18:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個月前的他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.69,0:18:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是代表之候有事發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.67,0:18:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.37,0:18:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来發生意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.84,0:18:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，那麽誰在操縱那傢伙！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.33,0:19:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布烈絲！快回来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.27,0:19:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時候我怎能回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.65,0:19:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.95,0:19:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…惡…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.15,0:19:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布烈絲！  手…手臂不動！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.22,0:19:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎辦！？我…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.56,0:19:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布烈絲怎麽了！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.39,0:19:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…惡…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.60,0:19:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…！手只要能動…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.20,0:19:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布烈絲小姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.33,0:19:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的左手稍為能動吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.80,0:19:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你用左手攻擊右手的肩膊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.21,0:19:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝擊應該會令回路再次接通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.28,0:19:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米奇…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.58,0:20:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把KNUCKLE…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.51,0:20:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BOMBER的威力降至3級
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.48,0:20:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不干涉她們的行動是我的規矩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.55,0:20:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要忘記今次是例外的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.52,0:20:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.96,0:20:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我知道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.24,0:20:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比爾！你是比爾吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.80,0:20:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.87,0:20:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来了吧！比爾！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.34,0:20:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…亞人…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.31,0:20:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛倫小姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.41,0:20:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丈夫一個月前遇上意外死了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.42,0:20:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.12,0:21:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.49,0:21:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使他未死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.26,0:21:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他今次畢竟也無心回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.93,0:21:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他今次有心回来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.66,0:21:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丈夫從今日起請了三星期假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.47,0:21:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且，他訂了兩張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.14,0:21:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去南海小島的飛機票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.28,0:21:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.81,0:21:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丈夫也訂了這個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.69,0:21:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【愛倫，我永遠愛你比爾】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.26,0:21:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定很想拿着那隻錶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.86,0:22:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来看你高興的表情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.23,0:22:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他未死的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.98,0:23:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LIVE STAGE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.52,0:24:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樂隊成員交換目光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.98,0:24:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨着喇叭的強勁節奏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.89,0:24:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,震撼人心的歌聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.09,0:24:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟市內響起的爆炸聲重疊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.99,0:24:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心跳飛快地加速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.19,0:24:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當舞台給染成鮮紅色時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.99,0:24:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射燈照着一個細小人影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.40,0:24:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.77,0:24:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回，吹波糖危機


